  "title": "Business Development Manager",
  "description": "<p>1. Candidate will be required to work with multiple teams across different countries in the Asia Pacific region on spearheading, planning, overseeing, managing, and improving all related brands under the company in the areas of but not limited to:</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>i. Product Marketing Management and Development (overseeing and execution)</strong></p><ul><li>Working with the company's Product Marketing Managers and overseas teams in various markets to plan, oversee and execute different agendas and activities.</li></ul><p><strong>ii. Events Planning and Management / Sponsorships (overseeing and execution)</strong></p><ul><li>Working with overseas teams to plan, oversee and execute any events that are organised by the company.</li><li>Sponsor management</li></ul><p><strong>iii. Suppliers / Principals Management</strong></p><ul><li>Building relations with overseas business teams and various partners in the countries under candidate's purview.</li><li>Team management</li><li>In-charge of ensuring the performance of overseas team members, working with Product Managers in markets under candidate's purview. Candidate to function as the HQ (Singapore)'s representative for all matters of business.</li></ul><p>2. Candidate will also be required to work with the Directors on Business Development projects, such as but not limited to:</p><p></p><p><strong>i. New Product Research and Development</strong></p><ul><li>Working with the Directors and Technical team on new product lines for every market</li><li>Deciding what suitable product lines will fit into the company's portfolio</li><li>Launching of new product lines</li></ul><p><strong>ii. Market studies for new international markets</strong></p><ul><li>Working with Directors on market feasibility studies for other countries where the company has yet to establish a presence.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 5 years of experience in Regional Sales/Marketing in Electronics / Semiconductors field</li><li>Min. Diploma in Engineering or equivalent / Degree in Engineering</li><li>Able to communicate effectively in English / Mandarin to liaise with Chinese suppliers and vendors</li><li>Salary will commensurate accordingly to experience & qualifications</li></ul>",
